{% extends '/base.html.twig' %}
{% set carousel_high = 110 %}

{% block stylesheets %}
    <style>
        #myCarousel.carousel {
            height: {{ carousel_high }}px;
        }
        #myCarousel .item {
            height: {{ carousel_high }}px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #333;
        }
    </style>
{% endblock stylesheets %}

{% block carousel %}
    {% include "/partials/carousel.html.twig" %}
{% endblock carousel %}

{% block body %}
    <h3><span class="cale" style="font-weight:bolder">EPAPERS</span> for sale</h3>
    <h5>Practical uses</h5>
        <ul style="font-weight:bolder">
            <li>Meeting room sign that updates every hour showing next meetings and attendees</li>
            <li>Living picture, showing events or <a href="{{ path('www_api-cloudwatch') }}">Cloudwatch statistics</a>. They are also great to show
                <a href="https://superrare.co" target="_blank">digital art using our web-service Gallery module</a>.</li>
            <li>Help screens at the side of your laptop, refreshing dynamic information every 10 minutes</li>
        </ul>
    <p>In order to create our epaper component <span class="cale" style="font-weight:bolder">CALE-IDF</span> we purchase some epapers that now are hanging in our studio and we
        would like to sell some of them. The prices are shown in Ethereum, but we accept
        <a href="https://www.paypal.com/paypalme/fasani" target="_blank">payments also with paypal</a> or wire transfers. This will help us to finance the web-service
        and also to add support for more epaper displays. Please note that real colors of the epaper might be slightly different than the pictures shown here.<br>
        <b>All this epapers cases are designed by us, build by hand with care, they are tested and shipped with an A4 page explaining how is the wiring made in case you want
        to flash a different firmware to it. They also have a battery, that is charged using USB, same as your phone and either a reset button or a power on/off small switch.</b> They can also be shipped with your desired WiFi access point and password, pointing to your Screen in <span class="cale" style="font-weight:bolder">CALE.es web-service</span>, provided you have an account with us.
    </p>
    <div class="row">
