                            <li><b>Refresh time:</b> Aprox. 7 seconds</li>
                            <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vvsPnjLEW0k">Refresh video</a></li>
                            <li><b>Size:</b> 100 x 125 x 21 mm</li>
